FBIS4-59751 "drnes096_j_94004" FBIS-NES-94-096 Daily Report 17 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Saudi Arabia Al-Bid Message Conveyed to Saudi King Fahd Al-Bid Message Conveyed to Saudi King Fahd EA1705192394 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network in English 1600 GMT 17 May 94 EA1705192394 Aden Yemeni Republic Radio Network English BFN [Text] The custodian of the two holy mosques, King Fahd Bin'-'Abd-al-'Aziz, received a letter from Dr. 'Ali Salim al-Bid, vice chairman of the Presidential Council. The letter was handed over by Mr. Salih Abu-Bakr Bin-Husaynun, the minister of oil and mineral wealth, while being received by King Fahd in his office yesterday at (?al-Yamamah) palace. The letter contained an explanation of the latest developments in Yemen and the initiative presented by the Yemeni Socialist Party to stop the infighting.
